data.description: NEW PRICE!!!!!!!  Sought After Historic North End Area. Come check out this beautiful classic home with it's timeless charm. The tree lined streets of Oak Hill Ave. with it's variety of gorgeous turn of the century homes is a place you want to call home. The home features a lovely oversize wrap around porch. As you enter the home you are welcomed by a large classic foyer and open stair case. Pocket doors, fire place, wood floors and lots of room for a growing family. 4 Bedrooms and 2-1/2 baths will accomodate everyone. With a walk up attic, almost the size of some homes gives you all the storage you'll ever need. Modern updated Kitchen, Formal Dining Room, Parlor, Living Room with two separate areas and Laundry all on the main floor. Fenced  back yard with alley access. Full basement for the workshop and more storage. Newer heat and central air system to keep you comfortable year round. Come see for yourself.
